<hr noshade="noshade" style="width: 200px;" />
<h2>IRC</h2>

<p>
Get help right away using #e, the Enlightenment channel on FreeNode
IRC.  Choose <b>irc.freenode.net</b> as your server and then join <b>#e</b>
with the <b>/join #e</b> command. Einen deutschsprachigen IRC
channel gibt es auch - <b>#e.de</b> auf FreeNode. Per gli utenti di lingua
italiana Ã¨ disponibile il canale <b>#e-it</b>.</p>

<hr noshade="noshade" style="width: 200px;" />
<h2>Bugs</h2>
<p>If you happen to come across a bug, missing feature or lack of
documentation feel free to report it in the <a 
href="http://trac.enlightenment.org/e/report">Enlightenment Trac</a>.</p>

<hr noshade="noshade" style="width: 200px;" />
